一個執行環境下都會建立兩個東西",[227,228,229,232],"ul",{},[230,231,189],"li",{},[230,233,234,235],{},"變數 ",[187,236,237],{},"this",[16,239,240,241,244,245,247,248,251],{},"那課程也有講到 JavaScript 會參照",[187,242,243],{},"外部環境","，那什麼是外部環境?拿函數 ",[27,246,146],{}," 來講，它的外部環境就是",[187,249,250],{},"全域執行環境","，就如課程簡報一樣。",[16,253,254],{},[159,255],{"alt":250,"src":256},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FqUXTrVJ.png",[16,258,259,260,262],{},"所以 ",[27,261,181],{}," 也是一樣。",[16,264,265],{},[159,266],{"alt":250,"src":267},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FpedcXBi.png",[16,269,270,271,273,274,204],{},"而這章節有一個重點，我們要如何辨別它會**參照哪一個外部環境?**這邊就跟這「詞彙環境」有關係了，以函數 ",[27,272,146],{}," 來講它的詞彙環境會在哪裡?可以思考一下我們是在什麼環境下建立函數 ",[27,275,146],{},[20,277,278],{"className":22,"code":23,"language":24,"meta":25,"style":25},[27,279,280,288,296,300,304,312,324,330,334,338,350],{"__ignoreMap":25},[30,281,282,284,286],{"class":32,"line":33},[30,283,37],{"class":36},[30,285,41],{"class":40},[30,287,45],{"class":44},[30,289,290,292,294],{"class":32,"line":48},[30,291,51],{"class":44},[30,293,54],{"class":40},[30,295,57],{"class":44},[30,297,298],{"class":32,"line":60},[30,299,63],{"class":44},[30,301,302],{"class":32,"line":66},[30,303,70],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":69},[30,305,306,308,310],{"class":32,"line":73},[30,307,37],{"class":36},[30,309,78],{"class":40},[30,311,45],{"class":44},[30,313,314,316,318,320,322],{"class":32,"line":83},[30,315,86],{"class":36},[30,317,89],{"class":44},[30,319,92],{"class":36},[30,321,96],{"class":95},[30,323,99],{"class":44},[30,325,326,328],{"class":32,"line":102},[30,327,41],{"class":40},[30,329,107],{"class":44},[30,331,332],{"class":32,"line":110},[30,333,63],{"class":44},[30,335,336],{"class":32,"line":115},[30,337,70],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":69},[30,339,340,342,344,346,348],{"class":32,"line":120},[30,341,123],{"class":36},[30,343,89],{"class":44},[30,345,92],{"class":36},[30,347,130],{"class":95},[30,349,99],{"class":44},[30,351,352,354],{"class":32,"line":135},[30,353,138],{"class":40},[30,35